**/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock
# ts-rs's `serde-json-impl` / `chrono-impl` / `uuid-impl` features emit
# external-type mirrors (e.g. `JsonValue.ts`, `NaiveDateTime.ts`) into
# a per-crate `bindings/` directory unconditionally — `#[ts(export_to
# = ...)]` only redirects the OWN types, not the impl-feature mirrors.
# Audit P1-3 IPC bindings live under
# `packages/nexus-extension-api/src/generated/ipc/`, so the leftover
# crate-local `bindings/` is a build-only artefact.
crates/*/bindings/
# cargo-sweep timestamp marker
sweep.timestamp
.DS_Store
*.swp
# LibreOffice lockfiles
.~lock.*#
.superpowers/
.claude/*
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json
**/SESSION_SUMMARIES.md
# Per-install plugin settings written by the Settings modal.
plugins/*/settings.json
# Node / pnpm — workspace-wide
node_modules/
shell/dist/
packages/*/dist/
